# Movement
map gD cd ~/Documents
map gd cd ~/Downloads
map gp cd ~/Pictures
map gc cd ~/.config
map gr cd ~/repos
map gv cd ~/Videos
map gs cd ~/.local/bin
map gt cd ~/.local/share/Trash/files


